        "specific quote nonce.",
        "",
        "Required Accounts:",
        "- state (Account): Program state PDA. Seed: [\"state\"].",
        "- used_nonce (Account): The `used_nonce` PDA. Seed: [\"used_nonce\", nonce].",
        "",
        "Parameters:",
        "- _params.nonce: The 32-byte nonce identifying the PDA to check.",
